FBIS4-9560 "dreeu082_i_94024" FBIS-EEU-94-082 Daily Report 27 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Roso Relieved, Appointed to Joint Command Roso Relieved, Appointed to Joint Command AU2704072794 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in Serbo-Croatian 0700 GMT 27 Apr 94 AU2704072794 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] The Presidential Council of so-called Herceg-Bosna in Mostar has decided to relieve General Ante Roso of his duties as chief of General Staff of the Croatian Defense Council [HVO]. Roso has been appointed to a military post in the joint command of the HVO and the Bosnia-Herzegovina Army. Major-General Milivoj Petkovic has been appointed chief of the HVO General Staff.
